WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 17=

01:38.900 --> 01:40.210
If my guess is right,

01:41.570 --> 01:43.020
you should be Han Yisu.

01:43.490 --> 01:44.570
Elder Han, right?

02:00.580 --> 02:02.820
(Li Sect Elder, Han Yisu)

02:02.850 --> 02:04.380
How did you find me?

02:04.820 --> 02:06.740
The Li Sect folks are useless.

02:07.100 --> 02:08.850
I heard Nie Hengcheng's third disciple

02:09.660 --> 02:12.340
is a master of Gu poison and traps.

02:12.980 --> 02:15.220
There is no other who can

02:15.220 --> 02:16.060
call forth Erosion Ants.

02:16.380 --> 02:17.940
If your father and grandfather

02:18.410 --> 02:21.380
had your courage and wits back then,

02:21.700 --> 02:23.100
things would not be as they are today.

02:23.410 --> 02:24.850
You're just a pawn

02:24.850 --> 02:26.220
Nie Zhe left here.

02:26.660 --> 02:28.890
What right do you have
to judge the Mu clan?

02:29.260 --> 02:31.100
You lost to my aunt back then.

02:32.500 --> 02:33.380
These legs of yours

02:33.820 --> 02:35.820
were cut off by her blade, right?

02:36.410 --> 02:38.130
The 21st Form of the Sunshine Blade.

02:38.410 --> 02:39.500
Sundering Heaven, Slaying Sun.

02:40.980 --> 02:42.850
You're Cai Pingshu's niece.

02:43.130 --> 02:43.980
Yes.

02:48.940 --> 02:50.850
Thank heavens.

02:51.100 --> 02:53.130
Cai Pingshu took my master's life.

02:53.500 --> 02:54.610
And crippled my legs.

02:55.380 --> 02:57.890
She made me live like
a walking corpse for fifteen years.

02:58.850 --> 02:59.730
Today,

03:00.890 --> 03:03.850
I can finally avenge my master!

03:06.850 --> 03:08.290
You think these tiny ants

03:09.570 --> 03:10.780
can really trap me?

03:11.730 --> 03:13.220
You won't make it out alive.

03:13.850 --> 03:15.540
You'll die for sure!

03:15.890 --> 03:17.690
What if I don't?

03:34.540 --> 03:36.130
- Zhao!
- Mr. Mu!

03:51.410 --> 03:52.250
- Mr. Mu!
- Zhao!

03:59.260 --> 04:01.010
Zhao!

04:05.100 --> 04:06.570
Hurry! Move the iron cage away!

04:20.410 --> 04:21.340
Zhao.

04:21.340 --> 04:22.180
Are you alright?

04:24.050 --> 04:24.890
I'm fine.

04:26.250 --> 04:27.090
Where are we?

04:29.800 --> 04:30.810
Beneath the Bliss Palace,

04:31.320 --> 04:32.410
an underground palace indeed.

04:45.980 --> 04:47.980
Tomb of the Mu Couple.

04:50.370 --> 04:51.580
My father told me that

04:52.100 --> 04:53.140
beneath the Bliss Palace

04:54.020 --> 04:55.340
lies an underground palace built by

04:55.700 --> 04:57.050
Mu Donglie, the 5th Chief of Li Sect.

04:58.170 --> 05:00.020
But I never knew he was married.

05:00.930 --> 05:02.730
Why would your ancestor

05:02.730 --> 05:04.140
build an underground palace
for no reason?

05:09.250 --> 05:10.540
His reign was short.

05:11.750 --> 05:12.780
According to sect records,

05:13.580 --> 05:14.660
before he turned twenty,

05:15.220 --> 05:16.410
he handed the Chief's seat

05:16.410 --> 05:17.810
to his nephew.

05:17.810 --> 05:18.950
Then he left and vanished

05:19.170 --> 05:20.010
without a trace.

05:20.540 --> 05:22.700
Seems that ancestor was quite carefree.

05:31.410 --> 05:32.250
Let's go.

05:32.700 --> 05:34.660
Let's check out
the Mu ancestor's underground palace.

05:36.340 --> 05:40.060
(Tomb of the Mu Couple)

05:55.020 --> 05:55.860
Shangguan!

05:58.920 --> 05:59.930
How is the Young Master?

06:00.140 --> 06:00.980
The trap's destroyed.

06:00.980 --> 06:02.290
We can only dig it open manually now.

06:02.720 --> 06:03.650
Have you found Nie Zhe?

06:04.250 --> 06:05.100
Not yet.

06:05.100 --> 06:06.340
We swept the whole palace area.

06:06.390 --> 06:07.780
It's surrounded tight
as a iron fortress.

06:08.050 --> 06:08.980
Where else could he go?

06:09.290 --> 06:10.130
How's the Xuanwu Altar?

06:10.580 --> 06:11.850
Yu Huiyin fled as soon as

06:11.950 --> 06:13.220
she heard the Bliss Palace fell.

06:13.220 --> 06:14.730
The other followers were forced to join.

06:15.220 --> 06:16.140
Once their leader ran,

06:16.370 --> 06:17.290
they surrendered too.

06:17.660 --> 06:19.130
Hurry, dig faster.

06:25.050 --> 06:27.340
Your ancestor's
underground palace is amazing.

06:27.810 --> 06:29.540
It loops endlessly, seamless in design.

06:29.920 --> 06:31.540
We've walked for a long time
and can't get out.

06:34.490 --> 06:35.340
I think this person

06:36.100 --> 06:37.250
was trapped here

06:37.520 --> 06:38.660
and took his own life in despair.

06:39.290 --> 06:40.130
Why did your ancestor

06:40.540 --> 06:41.540
go to

06:41.540 --> 06:42.730
all this trouble?

06:43.140 --> 06:44.100
Did the Demon Sect

06:44.580 --> 06:46.340
have too much money to burn?

06:46.900 --> 06:48.050
Sect records don't say

06:48.340 --> 06:49.180
why Chief Mu Donglie

06:49.540 --> 06:50.730
built the underground palace.

06:51.370 --> 06:52.610
But word in the sect has it

06:53.490 --> 06:54.850
that he left secret manuals here,

06:55.220 --> 06:56.060
along with treasure.

06:57.050 --> 06:57.890
So

06:58.290 --> 06:59.810
these bones are from a treasure hunter.

07:02.250 --> 07:03.220
Forget it.

07:03.220 --> 07:04.060
We're doomed anyway.

07:04.490 --> 07:05.850
Let's sit and rest.

07:18.510 --> 07:19.450
Do you fear death?

07:25.290 --> 07:26.220
Of course I do.

07:27.290 --> 07:28.490
But life is life.

07:29.140 --> 07:30.340
Birth and death are inevitable.

07:31.410 --> 07:32.250
Just accept it.

07:35.220 --> 07:36.060
What about you?

07:37.020 --> 07:37.860
Do you fear death?

07:43.120 --> 07:44.700
I was already a dead man walking anyway.

07:45.610 --> 07:46.780
As long as I kill Nie Zhe

07:47.850 --> 07:49.020
and take back the Li Sect

07:49.490 --> 07:50.340
before I die,

07:51.290 --> 07:52.730
even if we perish together,

07:53.900 --> 07:54.930
I'll never regret it.

07:58.660 --> 08:00.050
I just never thought

08:01.020 --> 08:02.140
you'd actually come.

08:05.700 --> 08:06.700
Now that you're in this world,

08:09.220 --> 08:10.210
I don't want to die anymore.

08:29.140 --> 08:30.250
My ancestor once came here.

08:32.510 --> 08:33.530
Look at this peach blossom.

08:33.980 --> 08:35.850
It has three layers of petals,
from inside to out.

08:36.180 --> 08:38.130
The innermost layer has just two petals.

08:38.490 --> 08:39.340
A signal?

08:39.340 --> 08:40.220
No.

08:40.220 --> 08:41.100
To be precise,

08:41.100 --> 08:42.250
it's a guide from Luoying Valley.

08:43.490 --> 08:44.340
Qian position, three.

08:44.890 --> 08:45.730
Yao position, two.

08:46.890 --> 08:47.730
Follow me.

08:57.490 --> 08:58.490
It's been fifteen years.

08:59.060 --> 09:00.820
Fifteen years,
and it hasn't changed a bit.

09:06.370 --> 09:07.250
I'm truly glad.

09:07.940 --> 09:09.180
It's been so well preserved.

09:12.010 --> 09:13.100
Good, very good.

09:16.650 --> 09:17.490
Elder Yan.

09:19.490 --> 09:20.330
Elder Yan!

09:23.820 --> 09:26.250
We invited you here to
help the Young Master.

09:28.850 --> 09:29.690
The trap closed.

09:29.750 --> 09:30.690
No way to dig it open.

09:30.850 --> 09:32.490
Do you know where it leads?

09:32.490 --> 09:33.330
Any other entrances?

09:37.300 --> 09:38.420
It should be

09:38.730 --> 09:40.060
Chief Mu Donglie's

09:40.380 --> 09:41.220
underground palace.

09:41.220 --> 09:42.060
Underground palace?

09:42.300 --> 09:43.140
What was it for?

09:49.890 --> 09:50.820
I've forgotten.

09:50.820 --> 09:53.340
I need to drink the Bliss Palace's
special wine to remember.

09:57.060 --> 09:57.900
The mechanism's here.

10:14.820 --> 10:16.940
To carve out such an underground world.

10:17.150 --> 10:18.730
That must have cost countless resources.

10:19.420 --> 10:20.340
Was your ancestor idle?

10:22.060 --> 10:22.900
He was far from idle.

10:23.820 --> 10:25.420
He took over the Li Sect at 13,

10:25.820 --> 10:27.420
fought all the way to
Thousandfold Cliff,

10:27.950 --> 10:29.180
nearly wiped out the Six Sects.

10:31.610 --> 10:33.420
Probably just Li Sect bragging.

10:37.180 --> 10:38.610
The carvings on this screen wall

10:39.340 --> 10:40.180
look like storybooks.

10:42.500 --> 10:43.890
It's the story of our founding ancestor,

10:44.820 --> 10:45.770
Mu Xiujue.

10:48.250 --> 10:51.010
(I lived at Thousandfold Cliff
as a child.)

10:51.490 --> 10:52.890
(The world was peaceful.)

10:52.890 --> 10:53.980
(Father raised me strictly.)

10:53.980 --> 10:55.530
(I trained day and night.)

10:55.530 --> 10:57.420
(Demons descended,
harming the innocent.)

10:57.850 --> 11:00.180
(I marched with Father
and fellow disciples from Beichen.)

11:00.180 --> 11:02.490
(Yet the demons were too powerful.)

11:02.490 --> 11:04.180
(We suffered heavy losses.)

11:04.180 --> 11:05.370
(To avenge them,)

11:05.370 --> 11:07.820
(I used forbidden technique
to control demons and fight back.)

11:08.650 --> 11:10.980
(Father was furious,
scolding me severely.)

11:12.060 --> 11:13.980
(We argued for months.)

11:13.980 --> 11:16.130
(Which made him fall ill.)

11:16.130 --> 11:17.220
(I knew I was unfilial.)

11:17.220 --> 11:18.530
(But I didn't think I was wrong.)

11:19.180 --> 11:22.180
(So I left Beichen
and went to Hanhai Mountains alone.)

11:23.890 --> 11:24.730
Oh my god!

11:25.580 --> 11:27.250
He was Beichen Founder's son.

11:28.730 --> 11:29.770
He left in a huff after

11:29.920 --> 11:30.900
a father-son falling-out

11:31.130 --> 11:32.060
and founded the Li Sect.

11:32.650 --> 11:34.060
And our Six Sects' founders

11:34.530 --> 11:35.580
were just six servants.

11:38.530 --> 11:39.490
I told you.

11:40.030 --> 11:41.610
There's no strict line
between good and evil.

11:42.200 --> 11:44.010
It's all made-up stories by descendants

11:44.010 --> 11:45.010
with schemes.

11:45.650 --> 11:46.580
Who's good? Who's evil?

11:47.730 --> 11:48.570
No one knows.

11:53.370 --> 11:54.370
Let's check over there.

12:20.010 --> 12:21.730
Did Mu Donglie build this

12:22.370 --> 12:23.530
just to hide a woman?

12:23.820 --> 12:25.010
The tombstone says

12:25.490 --> 12:26.650
"Tomb of the Mu Couple."

12:27.060 --> 12:27.900
Could

12:28.370 --> 12:30.060
they have lived here their whole lives?

12:30.420 --> 12:32.730
Why build a wedding chamber underground?

12:35.010 --> 12:37.730
Does the Li Sect always marry in secret?

12:43.220 --> 12:44.060
Don't worry.

12:44.220 --> 12:45.300
When I marry someday,

12:46.550 --> 12:47.890
I'll announce it to the whole world.

13:07.100 --> 13:07.940
Shiyun.

13:09.100 --> 13:09.940
Luo Shiyun?

13:09.980 --> 13:11.220
This sword belonged to Luo Shiyun.

13:11.890 --> 13:12.730
You know her?

13:13.220 --> 13:14.940
The second-generation demoness
of Luoying Valley.

13:15.650 --> 13:16.650
Extremely talented.

13:17.130 --> 13:19.490
The best swordsman
among the Six Sects back then.

13:19.670 --> 13:21.530
She was supposed to
marry the Lord of Qingque Sect,

13:22.250 --> 13:24.010
but she was tempted by a demon

13:24.620 --> 13:25.540
and ran away with him.

13:25.730 --> 13:27.580
Because of that,
she was branded a demoness.

13:27.820 --> 13:29.490
So that demon was Mu Donglie.

13:48.370 --> 13:49.530
All you Mu clan's are jerks!

13:50.340 --> 13:52.370
Did your clan lock up
my Luoying Valley ancestor here?

13:52.790 --> 13:54.060
What does something 100 years ago

13:54.700 --> 13:55.700
have to do with me?

13:55.700 --> 13:57.300
Can one "Mu" erase another?

13:57.980 --> 14:00.250
Who else am I gonna blame
for your ancestor's dirty deeds?

14:08.490 --> 14:10.180
Today marks the joyful start
of our union.

14:12.020 --> 14:13.340
May we stay together till old age,

14:13.770 --> 14:14.700
our resolve unshaken.

14:16.180 --> 14:17.370
We make this vow.

14:18.220 --> 14:19.060
You and I

14:20.520 --> 14:21.490
never betray each other.

14:24.730 --> 14:25.880
What are you saying?

14:30.500 --> 14:32.220
A marriage contract
between Luo Shiyun and Mu Donglie.

14:32.520 --> 14:33.450
Written by Luo Shiyun.

14:35.850 --> 14:37.650
If they truly loved each other,

14:38.100 --> 14:39.650
why did Mu Donglie lock her up?

14:40.580 --> 14:41.770
If you wish to know the answer,

14:43.220 --> 14:44.850
we'll have to read
Luo Shiyun's handbook.

14:47.650 --> 14:48.490
July 11th.

14:48.790 --> 14:50.730
Mu Donglie has been stationed
at the cliff base for months.

14:51.030 --> 14:52.220
The five sects are too busy to help.

14:52.530 --> 14:53.370
Rescue is hardly possible.

14:53.820 --> 14:55.730
Thousandfold Cliff could fall any day.

14:56.300 --> 14:57.940
So the records were true,

14:58.730 --> 14:59.700
Chief Mu Donglie

15:00.220 --> 15:01.770
almost wiped out the Six Sects.

15:02.150 --> 15:03.770
The Six Sects stood on
the brink of ruin.

15:04.490 --> 15:06.100
Killing the leader Mu Donglie

15:06.650 --> 15:07.490
will save them.

15:08.130 --> 15:09.100
But during the battle,

15:09.490 --> 15:10.730
his men ambushed me.

15:10.920 --> 15:12.130
I slipped and fell off the cliff.

15:12.580 --> 15:13.610
In that perilous moment,

15:13.610 --> 15:15.650
I pulled him down with a silver chain.

15:18.900 --> 15:21.660
(Luoying Valley, Luo Shiyun)

15:32.100 --> 15:32.940
Why?

15:32.940 --> 15:34.100
(Chief of Li Sect, Mu Donglie)

15:34.100 --> 15:35.100
Why didn't you kill me?

15:35.530 --> 15:36.940
This isn't how you should die.

15:40.180 --> 15:41.730
When both our wounds have healed,

15:43.100 --> 15:43.940
we'll duel again.

15:44.180 --> 15:45.130
It's a promise.

15:46.040 --> 15:47.770
♪In days gone by♪

15:48.080 --> 15:49.630
♪Willows swayed gently♪

15:49.930 --> 15:52.680
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

15:53.650 --> 15:54.840
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

15:54.850 --> 15:56.320
♪A fleeting glance♪

15:56.490 --> 15:57.400
♪And then♪

15:57.410 --> 16:00.360
♪Love consumed me♪

16:01.170 --> 16:02.720
♪Now I think of you♪

16:03.120 --> 16:04.760
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

16:05.020 --> 16:06.360
♪Alas, we parted♪

16:06.370 --> 16:08.560
♪Longing for your return♪

16:08.690 --> 16:09.640
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

16:09.650 --> 16:11.120
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

16:11.130 --> 16:12.160
♪Scattered petals♪

16:12.170 --> 16:14.400
♪Cover the ground♪

16:15.260 --> 16:17.720
♪Such should be our meeting♪

16:17.900 --> 16:22.580
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

16:22.600 --> 16:25.320
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

16:25.580 --> 16:29.520
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

16:30.240 --> 16:32.770
♪Such should be our meeting♪

16:33.050 --> 16:37.300
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

16:37.600 --> 16:40.180
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

16:40.560 --> 16:44.900
♪Tears are like pearls♪

16:45.820 --> 16:48.150
♪Things stay, yet you're away♪

16:48.530 --> 16:52.750
♪Who will hear the broken strings♪

16:53.290 --> 16:55.390
♪Across the starry skies♪

16:55.770 --> 17:00.650
♪I see your shadow there♪

17:00.810 --> 17:03.590
♪Such should be our meeting♪

17:03.590 --> 17:08.070
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

17:08.320 --> 17:10.930
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

17:11.720 --> 17:12.650
What's wrong with you?

17:13.770 --> 17:14.610
It's so cold.

17:15.810 --> 17:18.450
♪Such should be our meeting♪

17:18.620 --> 17:22.990
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

17:23.320 --> 17:25.810
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

17:26.810 --> 17:27.980
Don't leave me.

17:30.980 --> 17:31.820
Alright.

17:34.580 --> 17:36.970
♪Such should be our meeting♪

17:37.400 --> 17:40.650
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

17:42.170 --> 17:44.360
♪Such should be♪

17:45.030 --> 17:54.400
♪Our reunion♪

18:05.050 --> 18:05.890
Shiyun!

18:09.050 --> 18:09.890
Yin.

18:16.250 --> 18:17.530
I knew you would still be alive.

18:23.050 --> 18:23.890
Go check inside.

18:25.330 --> 18:26.290
Let's go back,

18:27.980 --> 18:28.820
Yin.

18:29.180 --> 18:30.140
(Qingque Sect, Yin)

18:30.140 --> 18:30.980
Alright.

18:47.290 --> 18:48.250
Soon after,

18:48.250 --> 18:50.490
Yin and I fulfilled our marriage vow.

18:50.840 --> 18:51.730
But unexpectedly,

18:51.730 --> 18:53.210
Mu Donglie came to steal me away.

18:53.620 --> 18:54.490
During the fight,

18:54.490 --> 18:56.620
he ambushed Yin with Chaos Needle.

19:05.070 --> 19:06.420
You've been hit by my Chaos Needle.

19:07.250 --> 19:08.090
Stop struggling.

19:09.770 --> 19:11.860
I hate people
who break their promises the most.

19:11.860 --> 19:13.380
You agreed to stay with me,

19:14.620 --> 19:17.250
but betrayed me
by marrying someone else.

19:17.250 --> 19:18.250
It is you who betrayed me.

19:38.490 --> 19:39.330
Don't!

19:41.860 --> 19:43.090
If you agree to stay,

19:44.860 --> 19:45.730
I'll let him go.

19:55.980 --> 19:57.010
I agree.

19:58.530 --> 19:59.380
Don't harm him.

20:06.860 --> 20:07.700
Die!

20:13.530 --> 20:14.380
I never thought

20:14.900 --> 20:16.250
the ancestors' love

20:16.980 --> 20:18.530
was so thrilling

20:18.530 --> 20:19.420
and touching.

20:21.490 --> 20:22.570
So Zhao,

20:23.230 --> 20:24.330
you like this intense stuff?

20:26.940 --> 20:28.140
Do you think my ancestor

20:28.770 --> 20:30.140
stayed with Mu Donglie

20:30.140 --> 20:31.720
willingly?

20:34.330 --> 20:35.170
Undo it.

20:37.490 --> 20:38.500
This is the underground palace

20:39.490 --> 20:40.330
with a maze outside.

20:40.730 --> 20:41.860
No guide,

20:41.860 --> 20:42.810
no way out.

20:43.530 --> 20:44.370
I'm not leaving.

21:25.900 --> 21:26.740
Stay and eat with me.

21:54.320 --> 21:56.220
I searched for a path
in the underground palace.

21:56.220 --> 21:57.730
Leaving behind the peach blossom mark.

21:58.330 --> 21:59.570
After great hardship,

21:59.570 --> 22:01.330
I finally returned to
Thousandfold Cliff.

22:01.810 --> 22:03.660
But Qingque Sect turned on me,

22:03.660 --> 22:07.570
accusing me of eloping with
the demon Mu Donglie.

22:08.140 --> 22:09.700
Even Yin suspected

22:10.250 --> 22:11.730
I was involved with Mu Donglie.

22:12.940 --> 22:14.420
I was heartbroken,

22:15.420 --> 22:16.570
unable to defend myself.

22:16.940 --> 22:18.050
To prove my innocence,

22:19.290 --> 22:20.660
I jumped off the cliff.

22:22.050 --> 22:23.980
How dare they slander my ancestor!

22:24.570 --> 22:26.090
Typical of them.

22:31.660 --> 22:32.530
But

22:32.940 --> 22:34.680
Mu Donglie saved me.

22:35.660 --> 22:36.570
Why save me?

22:36.860 --> 22:38.290
You already died for them.

22:38.700 --> 22:39.540
You owe them nothing.

22:40.290 --> 22:41.130
Stay here.

22:43.490 --> 22:44.810
Live with me.

23:07.770 --> 23:10.220
If we, like our ancestors,

23:11.700 --> 23:12.770
spent a lifetime here,

23:14.840 --> 23:15.780
wouldn't that be joyful?

23:16.420 --> 23:17.530
Don't you feel

23:18.490 --> 23:19.900
this place is like a cage?

23:20.380 --> 23:21.490
Even if it is a cage,

23:22.290 --> 23:23.810
if I can be with the one I love,

23:24.220 --> 23:25.490
it would still be sweet as honey.

23:29.700 --> 23:32.010
The daughters of Luoying Valley
love the bustle.

23:33.180 --> 23:34.570
Living underground

23:35.090 --> 23:36.660
away from relatives.

23:37.180 --> 23:38.290
How lonely that would be.

23:39.330 --> 23:40.700
Even if she agreed at first,

23:41.290 --> 23:42.530
she'd regret it later.

23:43.860 --> 23:44.860
Mu Qingyan,

23:44.860 --> 23:45.700
remember.

23:46.530 --> 23:48.090
Joy inside a cage

23:48.660 --> 23:49.940
is never true joy.

23:50.700 --> 23:51.730
Where love begins,

23:53.290 --> 23:54.250
it runs deep.

23:54.760 --> 23:55.810
Never bending to setbacks.

23:56.380 --> 23:58.700
If you regret and back out later,

23:59.530 --> 24:00.660
what am I supposed to do?

24:02.770 --> 24:03.770
All I know is,

24:03.770 --> 24:05.050
if we can't find our way out,

24:05.050 --> 24:06.140
we'll starve to death here.

24:23.250 --> 24:24.090
Smells good.

24:35.980 --> 24:37.250
I remember now.

24:37.660 --> 24:38.620
This underground palace

24:39.010 --> 24:40.180
has no exit at all.

24:40.660 --> 24:42.530
I've served as Elder Zhibi

24:42.530 --> 24:43.370
for all these years,

24:43.860 --> 24:47.570
never heard of anyone escaping alive.

24:52.120 --> 24:52.980
For now,

24:52.980 --> 24:54.050
seal all news and

24:54.050 --> 24:54.890
watch Nie Zhe's men.

24:55.140 --> 24:55.980
They're still alive.

24:56.570 --> 24:57.410
Elder Yan,

24:57.980 --> 25:00.220
can you find all historical records of

25:00.220 --> 25:01.490
the underground palace's construction?

25:02.380 --> 25:03.570
You're thinking...

25:03.860 --> 25:05.050
Even a Tomb Chamber

25:05.050 --> 25:06.010
has secret passageways,

25:06.010 --> 25:06.900
let alone an underground palace.

25:07.420 --> 25:08.260
Yes, exactly.

25:08.570 --> 25:10.860
So there must be another exit.

25:11.660 --> 25:14.050
Mu Donglie claimed
he sealed the underground palace,

25:14.980 --> 25:15.900
but I believe

25:16.180 --> 25:17.490
there's definitely another way out.

25:17.900 --> 25:19.730
Otherwise, my ancestral grandmother

25:19.730 --> 25:22.290
wouldn't have left
the guide to Luoying Valley.

25:30.700 --> 25:32.090
There's another guide hidden here.

25:47.290 --> 25:48.530
Now I believe

25:48.810 --> 25:49.650
those two elders

25:50.050 --> 25:51.200
must have left early

25:51.520 --> 25:52.660
and lived happily ever after.

25:54.770 --> 25:55.610
Watch out!

26:12.230 --> 26:13.170
Mr. Mu, are you alright?

26:14.220 --> 26:15.220
Glad to hear you're fine.

26:15.220 --> 26:16.220
His swordsmanship is weird.

26:16.620 --> 26:17.860
I've never seen this style.

26:18.140 --> 26:19.770
No one in the Li Sect
has moves like this.

26:20.530 --> 26:22.530
Could Nie Zhe
have brought the helper outside?

26:35.900 --> 26:37.050
We're finally alive.

26:37.700 --> 26:38.730
Zhao and Mr. Mu

26:38.920 --> 26:40.490
were trapped in
the underground palace so long.

26:40.980 --> 26:41.900
Did anything happen?

26:44.660 --> 26:45.770
It was just a big maze

26:46.420 --> 26:47.930
Wandered around and got out.

26:48.730 --> 26:49.570
And you?

26:50.220 --> 26:51.940
How did you find the exit?

26:52.490 --> 26:54.090
When Shangguan and I
studied old records,

26:54.340 --> 26:56.660
we found a legend about
the Underground Palace construction.

26:57.540 --> 26:59.410
They said the mountain's fengshui
was strange.

26:59.720 --> 27:01.070
The water source dried up suddenly.

27:01.530 --> 27:03.180
And ghosts were said to
wander the woods.

27:04.680 --> 27:07.220
I suspected digging
the secret passageways

27:07.220 --> 27:08.570
cut off the underground water.

27:09.190 --> 27:10.490
So we followed the mountain's terrain,

27:10.940 --> 27:12.530
deduced the palace's layout,

27:12.820 --> 27:14.090
and finally locked onto the location.

27:14.490 --> 27:15.770
If you weren't a young hero,

27:16.140 --> 27:17.660
you could've become a detective instead.

27:18.810 --> 27:20.940
By the way, found Nie Zhe?

27:20.940 --> 27:22.570
We set up checkpoints
all over Hanhai Mountains.

27:23.940 --> 27:24.810
No sign of him.

27:32.490 --> 27:33.330
Mr. Dai,

27:33.470 --> 27:35.290
Shangguan just opened
the Bliss Palace's treasury.

27:35.290 --> 27:37.290
He invites you to
find the Jade Sunflower together.

27:39.900 --> 27:40.740
Thank you.

27:45.720 --> 27:46.570
How is it?

27:46.570 --> 27:47.420
How's the wonton?

27:48.570 --> 27:49.700
Do you think Nie Zhe

27:51.420 --> 27:53.980
dug a secret passageways and ran?

27:54.700 --> 27:55.770
Mu Donglie already turned

27:55.770 --> 27:57.400
the Bliss Palace's underground
into a palace.

27:57.860 --> 27:59.090
Where would he dig another?

28:00.730 --> 28:01.570
Good point.

28:02.530 --> 28:03.900
But I told You Guanyue

28:03.900 --> 28:05.490
to seal all checkpoints.

28:05.490 --> 28:07.180
Even if Nie Zhe could fly,

28:07.180 --> 28:08.490
he can't get out.

28:10.090 --> 28:11.490
So where is he hiding?

28:11.860 --> 28:13.220
From reading

28:13.220 --> 28:14.570
800 storybooks,

28:15.290 --> 28:16.700
people hide in only three places.

28:17.020 --> 28:17.930
The forbidden grounds.

28:18.420 --> 28:19.260
The ancestral shrine.

28:19.700 --> 28:20.540
And under the bed.

28:31.530 --> 28:34.140
This is where my father
lived as a child,

28:34.140 --> 28:35.700
the Mu clan's old residence.

28:36.620 --> 28:37.810
After my grandfather passed,

28:37.810 --> 28:39.330
Father wanted to avoid power struggles,

28:39.840 --> 28:41.490
so he moved to
Huanglao Peak's Carefree Chamber.

28:42.520 --> 28:44.420
Nie Hengcheng refused to
live on Mu Clan lands,

28:44.770 --> 28:46.730
so he built a new palace
at the Bliss Palace.

28:49.070 --> 28:50.570
This became Li Sect's forbidden ground.

28:51.020 --> 28:52.770
The Mu clan is a thorn
in the Nie clan's side

28:53.980 --> 28:55.220
I suppose no one dares come here

28:56.090 --> 28:57.180
to avoid suspicion.

29:12.010 --> 29:12.850
Zhao.

29:13.010 --> 29:15.730
Those 800 storybooks
weren't for nothing.

29:26.380 --> 29:27.810
How dare you hit me?

29:29.010 --> 29:30.900
Uncle Nie, hurry and tell me.

29:31.250 --> 29:33.090
Why did you slaughter Chang Fort?

29:33.770 --> 29:34.610
Why

29:35.140 --> 29:36.420
kill my father?

29:38.520 --> 29:39.620
What's the point of knowing?

29:40.330 --> 29:41.620
What's the point of winning?

29:41.620 --> 29:42.810
You'll be dead soon enough.

29:43.050 --> 29:43.890
True.

29:44.220 --> 29:46.250
So I'll do anything.

29:46.730 --> 29:48.380
Uncle Nie, best you cooperate.

29:48.920 --> 29:49.890
Save yourself the pain.

29:50.180 --> 29:51.530
I'll tell you nothing.

29:52.180 --> 29:55.290
I'll make you die in the dark.

29:56.700 --> 29:58.530
I learned a new martial art.

29:59.290 --> 30:00.660
It's super brutal.

30:01.020 --> 30:02.810
If I channel my inner power
into someone's meridians,

30:03.490 --> 30:04.700
this person will

30:05.570 --> 30:06.770
be unable to live,

30:07.490 --> 30:08.660
nor find release in death.

30:14.380 --> 30:15.730
How does it feel, Uncle Nie?

30:15.980 --> 30:16.820
Speak...

30:17.220 --> 30:18.060
or

30:18.940 --> 30:19.780
not?

30:20.330 --> 30:21.420
Just kill me.

30:23.620 --> 30:25.660
This power will stay in your body.

30:26.220 --> 30:27.220
The pain will get worse

30:27.660 --> 30:28.500
every Chou hour

30:29.380 --> 30:30.940
and Mao hour.

30:32.050 --> 30:32.980
How could Mu Zhengming

30:32.980 --> 30:34.700
have a son so twisted?

30:36.660 --> 30:37.900
I am not like my father.

30:39.010 --> 30:40.220
I can wait with you

30:40.940 --> 30:42.010
till Chou hour.

30:55.010 --> 30:55.850
Mr. Mu.

30:56.010 --> 30:56.850
What is it?

30:57.090 --> 30:57.930
Madam, she...

31:01.250 --> 31:02.090
Qingyan!

31:02.660 --> 31:03.900
Please forgive your mother.

31:04.490 --> 31:05.900
I was born timid by nature.

31:05.900 --> 31:07.860
It's all that scoundrel Nie Zhe.

31:07.860 --> 31:09.380
He pushed me into a corner.

31:09.380 --> 31:11.380
I had no choice

31:11.380 --> 31:13.620
but to do those stupid things.

31:13.620 --> 31:16.330
I regret it so much, my son.

31:16.860 --> 31:18.490
I was afraid of losing you.

31:18.490 --> 31:19.530
Don't joke, Madam.

31:20.770 --> 31:23.490
You're a spy trained
by the Demonic Camp.

31:23.490 --> 31:24.620
You're not this cowardly.

31:25.010 --> 31:26.420
Even if Nie Zhe

31:26.420 --> 31:27.530
threatened you,

31:27.860 --> 31:29.250
if you really wanted to warn me,

31:29.900 --> 31:30.980
one glance,

31:31.530 --> 31:32.370
one sentence,

31:33.290 --> 31:34.530
you could have found a way.

31:35.090 --> 31:35.930
But you didn't.

31:40.330 --> 31:42.180
If you'd only poisoned me,

31:43.490 --> 31:45.090
I might have let it go.

31:45.090 --> 31:45.930
But

31:47.700 --> 31:49.810
why poison my father?

31:52.730 --> 31:54.290
If you don't tell the truth,

31:55.770 --> 31:57.490
I'll make you taste

31:57.810 --> 31:59.570
the Suzi Fragrance Poison.

32:00.730 --> 32:01.570
Qingyan.

32:02.140 --> 32:02.980
I am your mother.

32:02.980 --> 32:04.250
And I was once your son.

32:05.620 --> 32:08.940
My father was once your husband.

32:11.810 --> 32:12.900
It was Nie Zhe.

32:13.770 --> 32:15.330
He ordered me to kill your father.

32:16.050 --> 32:17.250
Nie Zhe was jealous.

32:18.090 --> 32:19.290
He just became Chief,

32:19.750 --> 32:21.990
yet his skills and reputation
were no match for your father's.

32:22.530 --> 32:24.140
He knew I cared about your father.

32:24.820 --> 32:25.860
Jealousy clouded his mind.

32:26.420 --> 32:28.220
And he kept forcing me into it.

32:30.730 --> 32:32.900
If I didn't poison your father,

32:34.010 --> 32:35.570
he'd have me violated.

32:36.180 --> 32:38.050
I was truly terrified.

32:38.490 --> 32:40.090
I only thought of saving myself.

32:41.980 --> 32:42.980
Qingyan.

32:42.980 --> 32:44.380
I know I was wrong.

32:44.940 --> 32:46.900
I truly know my mistake.

32:52.980 --> 32:53.820
Shangguan.

33:01.570 --> 33:02.410
Chief Nie.

33:03.420 --> 33:05.700
I didn't expect you to be so petty.

33:05.700 --> 33:07.290
Even worse than a woman.

33:08.460 --> 33:09.380
Uncle Nie.

33:10.470 --> 33:11.660
Do you have something to say?

33:13.570 --> 33:15.810
It was your greed for vanity.

33:15.810 --> 33:17.810
You threw yourself into my arms.

33:17.810 --> 33:19.460
If you hadn't shamelessly clung to me,

33:19.460 --> 33:21.050
I'd never have looked twice at

33:21.050 --> 33:23.180
a promiscuous old hag like you.

33:26.380 --> 33:27.220
Liar!

33:27.570 --> 33:28.860
You seduced me first!

33:28.870 --> 33:29.770
Bah!

33:29.770 --> 33:30.860
Who'd seduce you?

33:30.860 --> 33:32.330
You hated Mu Zhengming

33:32.940 --> 33:34.570
for being indifferent to power and fame.

33:34.860 --> 33:36.620
And kept urging me to eliminate him.

33:36.900 --> 33:38.290
Someone like you, who harms her own son

33:38.290 --> 33:39.570
without a trace of mercy,

33:39.940 --> 33:41.140
doesn't deserve to be loved.

33:41.140 --> 33:42.730
What do you mean I urged you?

33:42.730 --> 33:44.730
It was the Man in Black who ordered you.

33:44.730 --> 33:46.360
He told you to attack the Chang Fort

33:46.360 --> 33:47.250
and find something.

33:47.250 --> 33:48.090
Shut up!

33:55.490 --> 33:56.490
Man in Black,

33:57.290 --> 33:58.220
who is he?

33:58.220 --> 34:00.090
There is no Man in Black.

34:00.090 --> 34:01.700
I fought him myself.

34:01.700 --> 34:04.090
Why would he order you to
attack the Chang Fort?

34:04.620 --> 34:06.290
What is he looking for?

34:16.980 --> 34:19.090
If the Man in Black is
really pulling the strings,

34:20.980 --> 34:22.300
I might spare you.

34:22.940 --> 34:24.130
Since he stays silent, I'll speak.

34:31.081 --> 34:41.741
=Generation to Generation=

35:00.501 --> 35:04.911
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

35:05.476 --> 35:10.091
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

35:10.431 --> 35:14.996
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

35:15.521 --> 35:19.821
♪Free to wander in the world♪

35:22.766 --> 35:27.466
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:27.991 --> 35:32.281
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

35:32.941 --> 35:36.971
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

35:37.286 --> 35:42.411
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

35:42.986 --> 35:47.796
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:48.011 --> 35:52.181
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

35:52.906 --> 35:56.841
♪I freely roam in the world♪

35:57.341 --> 36:02.616
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

36:25.346 --> 36:30.476
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:30.841 --> 36:35.211
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:35.476 --> 36:39.606
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:39.791 --> 36:45.366
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
